id: examples/stuck
title: "I feel stuck"
kind: example
status: example

current: "I keep circling the same problem."
possible: "I can see one small next move."
lacuna: "I do not know what is actually blocking movement."

move: "Write down the pattern without trying to solve it."
boundary: "Do not force a conclusion."
proof: "I can name the blocker more clearly after writing."
replay: "What changed after I observed it?"

